.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH config 1  "config " 
.SH NAME
config \- Show or update local configuration
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBconfig\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show or update local configuration
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
config\-set(1)
Set a configuration value
.TP
config\-show(1)
Show configuration, optionally limited to a section
.TP
config\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
